# Stripe API Keys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_PRICE_ID=price_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# App URL
APP_URL=https://your-app-domain.com

# 設定方法:
# 1. このファイルを .env にコピー
# 2. Stripeダッシュボードから各値を取得して設定
# 3. Vercelにデプロイ時は Environment Variables に設定

# Stripe設定手順:
# 1. https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys で Secret Key を取得
# 2. https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/products で商品・価格を作成（月額980円）
# 3. Price ID (price_xxx) をコピー
# 4. https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/webhooks で Webhook を作成
# 5. イベント選択:
#    - checkout.session.completed
#    - customer.subscription.created
#    - customer.subscription.updated
#    - customer.subscription.deleted
#    - invoice.payment_succeeded
#    - invoice.payment_failed
# 6. Webhook Secret (whsec_xxx) をコピー
